---
title: Baked Kumara & Mushroom Risotto with Toasted Pecans & Parmesan
description: Kumara goes a long way in this hearty meal. Roast it first before stirring it into a creamy, cheesy baked risotto for a rich flavour that will change the way you think about this humble Italian rice dish.

*Unfortunately, this week's pine nuts were in short supply, so we've replaced them with pecans. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/baked-kumara-mushroom-risotto-f0380589.jpg
